=Description=


"This podcast from the Center for Citizen Media features a conversation with Travis Henry of Yourhub.com. Yourhub allows residents of the Front Range region of Colorado to sign up to post their own news items and photos.

Travis also touches on efforts to syndicate the technology that powers Yourhub to other media organizations."
